  "original_title": "\u0baa\u0ba4\u0bb5\u0bbf \u0bb5\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0b95\u0bc1\u0bb5\u0ba4\u0bc8 \u0baa\u0bbf\u0bb0\u0ba4\u0bae\u0bb0\u0bcd \u0bb0\u0ba3\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bbf\u0b9f\u0bae\u0bcd \u0b89\u0bb1\u0bc1\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0b9f\u0bc1\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0ba9\u0bbe\u0bb0\u0bcd \u0b9c\u0ba9\u0bbe\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0baa\u0ba4\u0bbf \u0b95\u0bcb\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bbe",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "President Kota confirmed his resignation to Prime Minister Ranil",
      "author": "",
      "body_lines": [
        "President Gotabaya Rajapaksa has assured Prime Minister Ranil Wickremesinghe that he will step down as he promised earlier.",
        "The President had left the Presidential Palace after the public demonstration against the government on Saturday 9th.",
        "Following this, President Gotabaya Rajapaksa had informed Speaker Mahinda Yappa Abeywardena that he would resign from the presidency on Wednesday the 13th.",
        "In this case, it is noteworthy that President Gotabaya Rajapaksa has now confirmed to Prime Minister Ranil Wickremesinghe that he will resign as he announced earlier."
      ],
